This plugin adds the ability to ''automatically close Tags''. It needs the latest [[CodeMirror plugin|$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror]] to be installed

>To enable the Auto-Close Tags ~AddOn, copy the following lines and ''append'' them at the bottom of the ''require'' section in $:/config/CodeMirror<br>

>Then make sure that all entries except the last one within the ''require'' section end with a 'semicolon'<br>

<$macrocall $name="copy-to-clipboard-above-right" src='		"$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror/addon/fold/xml-fold.js",
		"$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror/addon/edit/closetag.js"'/>

```json
		"$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror/addon/fold/xml-fold.js",
		"$:/plugins/tiddlywiki/codemirror/addon/edit/closetag.js"
```

>Then ''append'' the following line to the ''configuration'' section in $:/config/CodeMirror<br>

<$macrocall $name="copy-to-clipboard-above-right" src='		"autoCloseTags": true'/>

```json
		"autoCloseTags": true
```

>''Save'' and ''Reload'' your wiki to have the changes take effect
